so i've had all this time to think (being grounded and all) and yea..so all this random stuff about me i keep thinking about. - livejournal isnt great(at all-so why do i continue it?). - I hate liars.(so much) - I REALLY like hugs. - and I REALLY like kisses on the cheek. - Trust is a big deal to me. - I don't like being alone. - Meaning when I move out I Will have a room-mate. - Sometimes I fall a lil harder than I should. - When it seems I'm ok, I'm usually not-just don't want you to see me hurt. - If I don't have anything to take a picture of, I tend to point it towards me. - I am extremely self-concious about myself(and my body). - I am TOO skinny(its gross). - My self-esteem isn't always too high. - I repeat myself. - Fish is gross to me. - Love is over-rated(or maybe I am just jealous of those who have it). - Its ridiculous how shy I am in front of some people and not others. - I have regrets. - I need more friends. - Certain things hurt me, and I deny it when you ask me. - I feel completely blank right now. - I hate knowing I can't do anything about something so small. - The habit of biting my nails, bothers me. - I don't wear skirts because I look at my legs and say, "ew".(even if the skirt is to my knees) - I get jealous, sometimes I just can't help it. - I would rather you be up front with me than hide something cause you think it will hurt me. - I don't make my bed, ever. - Watching a romantic comedy is needed sometimes. - Talking on the phone to certain people just put me in better moods, even if my mood sucks. - Certain people just make me smile. - I might be addicted to caffeine. - I do random dance movements with my mom(occasionaly). - I don't think I've ever been in love, but i was close(i think). it keeps going but i won't bore you considering most of you are skipping through this anyway. and because you had to endure this bull shizz of mine i end it with pictures. Hey You,
i have thought about this. looooong and hard. REALLY
i told you i wouldnt make a bunch of dumb posts and what not.(so i wont)
but this might be an exception.
and considering its my lj and barely anyone reads it anyway. o well.

i wont say i hate you. cause i dont.
i will say it hurt. but i wont say im not going to be ok. (cause i will..eventually)
i've learned alot from this.so i will thank you for that.
for instance..
-i trust people TOO easily.
-if i put 2 and 2 together i should talk to you about 4 (no one will probly get this,but thats ok. I do and thats what matters)
-if something happens once dont be to sure it wont happen again.
-shitty situations..well damnit, they will most likely end up shitty.
-i guess what happened(you know) i wouldnt consider a mistake or regret and im not going to apologize for it happening, just something i got over with. and can now go for ROUND 2! whether or not its you!..haha..just kidding..
______

deep down i think you are a great person. I'm sure you didnt mean for it to end up like this. Just happened, what can you do about it, right? If its what is going to make you happy, do it, make yourself happy before trying to make others happy. I still want to hang out, because we are still friends(meaning we can still be cool and just have fun) and we being as awesome as we are, we should do that sometime. I just hope the decision you made, was the right one, one that came from the heart and is how you feel. If so, I'm fine.
Thats all.

______

p.s.- Jessica Rogers, I really love you girl. I'm glad your always there for me (esp. when people who are suppose to be there for me are too busy with boys). We need to hang out morrrrrrre because I miss you and im SICK of it! hah..much <3 to you jessica your so awesome and great. I really mean it.
______

P.S.S.-thanks to you for talking to me when I couldn't talk to her because of her PHONE. Made me feel a lil better.
______
Don't worry i won't dwell on it, i'm sure you dont want me to, and i'm sure your not either.
